column1: ...Bridget Moynahan (born Kathryn Bridget Moynahan; April 28, 1971) is an American actress and model.  She graduated from Longmeadow High School, in Massachusetts, in 1989, and began pursuing a career in modeling.  She appeared in department-store catalogs and magazines, and after doing television commercials, she began taking acting lessons.  Moynahan made her television debut in a guest appearance in the comedy series Sex and the City in 1999, where she later had a recurring role...
